<p>
  <span class="nym">Bleddyn</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A derivative of <span class="lang">Old Breton</span>, <span class="lang">Middle Welsh</span> <i>bleid</i> 'wolf'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


<dl>
<dt><span class="area">Wales</span></dt>
<dd>
<dl>
<dt><span class="lang">Latin</span></dt>
